creator: Z & K Games
descriptionHtml:
Experience the thrill of Scary Teacher Multiplayer Game!
Find yourself trapped with miss T. Good thing is now your friends can join you and escape miss T together.
Scary Teacher is back with a high school camping adventure! On an annual camping trip, All students are going forcibly by Miss T to a horror and spooky place where nobody is allowed to be roaming around. Everybody is locked in the mysterious camping area.
Plan an escape from this haunted place. Now you can take your ideal revenge with your real friends which Miss T will never ever forget!

Find the hidden keys to unlock the main Gate. Assemble your squad for this adventurous mission.
You have limited time if you fail to go out, she will find you and punish you.Be careful Miss T hears everything as usual.

-Friends Squad
Let your friends join you and play together
-Miss T the hunter
Play as miss t and catch the little kids from escaping

Features
-Exciting 5 v 1 mode
-Thrilling arena to explore
-Unique weapons to choose from
-Play as a hunter or survivor
